{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-learn-what-the-company-does/task-1","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":[],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"es-a1-learn-what-the-company-does","challengeType":19,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>U ovom vežbanju, Sebastián govori o kompaniji. Pošto je 'kompanija' imenica u jedlini, koristi se oblik glagola trećeg lica, jednine.</p>\n<p>Glagol <span class=\"highlighted-text\">es</span> potiče od <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ser</span> (\"kuwa\").</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Es</span> koristi se zajedno sa <span class=\"highlighted-text\">él</span> / <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ella</span> / <span class=\"highlighted-text\">usted</span>, i takođe sa jedničkim imenicama kao <span class=\"highlighted-text\">la empresa</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">el equipo</span>, ili naziv kompanije.</p>\n<p>Kada spomenete kompaniju ili po imenu jednine, koristite <span class=\"highlighted-text\">es</span> jer je subjekt trećeg lica jednine. Primer:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Andes Commerce es una empresa internacional.</span> - Andes Commerce je međunarodna kompanija.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">La oficina es grande.</span> - Kancelarija je velika.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">El proyecto es importante.</span> - Projekat je važan.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":"<section id=\"explanation\">\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Andes Commerce es una empresa de tecnología</span> to znači \"Andes Commerce je tehnološka kompanija\".</p>\n<p>Vrsta glagola <span class=\"highlighted-text\">es</span> od glagola <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ser</span> (\"biti\") koristi se ovde jer rečenica opisuje kompaniju. Na primer:</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">La empresa es pequeña.</span> - Kompanija je mala.</p>\n</section>","helpCategory":"Spanish Curriculum","instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Slušajte audio odgovor na pitanje ispod.</p>\n</section>","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-learn-what-the-company-does/task-1"},"questions":[{"text":"<p>Koji glagol tačno odgovara subjektu \"Andes Commerce\" u ovoj rečenici?</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Soy</span></p>","feedback":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Soy</span> je prva osoba jedinice (<span class=\"highlighted-text\">yo</span>). Tema u ovoj vežbi nije \"ja\".</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Es</span></p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Eres</span></p>","feedback":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Eres</span> koristi se sa <span class=\"highlighted-text\">tú</span>. Ova rečenica nije namijenjena samo jednoj osobi.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Somos</span></p>","feedback":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Somos</span> je prva množinska osoba (<span class=\"highlighted-text\">nosotros</span>). \"Andes Commerce\" je jednina.</p>","audioId":null}],"solution":2}],"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company1-reception.png","characters":[{"character":"Sebastián","position":{"x":50,"y":18,"z":1.5},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"ES_A1_what_the_company_does.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":0.36,"finishTimestamp":3.7},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Sebastián","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Sebastián","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":4.34,"dialogue":{"text":"Andes Commerce es una empresa de tecnología.","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Sebastián","position":null,"opacity":0,"startTime":4.84,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null}]},"superBlock":"a1-professional-spanish","tests":[],"title":"Vežba 1","transcript":null,"translationPending":false,"videoId":null,"videoLocaleIds":null}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/#es-a1-learn-what-the-company-does","dashedName":"task-1","certification":"a1-professional-spanish","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"a1-professional-spanish","chapter":"es-a1-chapter-describing-company-and-people","module":"es-a1-module-describing-a-company","block":"es-a1-learn-what-the-company-does","isFirstStep":true,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-learn-what-the-company-does/task-2","prevChallengePath":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-warm-up-describing-a-company-basics/task-12","id":"69b03f6d56b08d3ed3e3105d","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":22,"challengeFiles":[]}},"id":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-learn-what-the-company-does/task-1"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}